s a solutions architect, enterprise architect, or consulting delivery architect working in on-prem and cloud-based environments. Good balance of strategic and tactical skills; high level of mental agility and capacity for original thought. Intermediate-level scripting/coding in Bash and Python. Experience implementing and working in a continuous integration (CI) or continuous development (CD) pipeline. Broad and deep technical experience with one or more virtualization and cloud technologies like VMware vSphere, Microsoft Hyper-V, Amazon Web Services (AWS), or Microsoft Azure. Experience with popular cloud platforms such as AWS, Azure, and GCP. Knowledge of container management and orchestration tools. Comfortable working with highly distributed teams. Open to 20-30% travel. Confidence to believe in yourself. Additional Information All your information will be kept confidential according to EEO guidelines Equal Opportunity Employer Veterans/Disabled Show full job description Apply Now Stay Connected Contact Us SimplyHired Blog Facebook Twitter LinkedIn YouTube Job Tools Local Jobs Salary Estimator Post Jobs Free Resume Builder Browse All Jobs All Salaries All Cities All Companies Guides Resumes Cover Letters Interviews Careers Take your job search wherever you go. United States United StatesCanada ArgentinaAustraliaBelgiÃ«BrasilDeutschlandEspaÃ±aFranceIndiaIrelandItaliaMÃ©xicoNederlandÃsterreichPortugalSchweizSouth AfricaSverigeUnited KingdomÐ Ð¾ÑÑÐ¸Ñíêµ­ä¸­å½æ¥æ¬ Â© 2020 SH Inc. | Privacy | TermsÂ |Â Privacy Center |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
